State Council Information Office Releases White Paper on &quot; China and the World in the New Era &quot;
On the occasion of the 70th anniversary of the founding of the People &apos;s Republic of China , the State Council Information Office released the White Paper &quot; China and the World in the New Era &quot; on 27 July .
