The protection of women &apos;s legitimate rights and interests embodies respect for and protection of human rights , and is also an important symbol of social civilization and progress .
On September 27 , at the 15th Session of the Standing Committee of the 12th National People &apos;s Congress of the Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region , the Regulations on the Protection of the Rights and Interests of Women in the Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region were adopted by a high vote .
