Article 44 of the Ordinance expressly prohibits the frequent sexual abuse of girls and requires educational institutions to carry out education , protection and prevention , which is a new benchmark for the protection of girls in local legislation .
With regard to women &apos;s right to know and dispose of the joint property of marriage and family , article 35 of the Regulations clearly stipulates women &apos;s right to know about the joint property and the obligations of property registration agencies and related subjects , thus providing solid institutional support for women &apos;s right to defend their rights .
Moreover , in response to a topical social issue of gender discrimination in employment , article 26 of the Ordinance prohibits not only direct but also indirect discrimination , and draws on recent experience in the practice of joint interviews to strengthen sanctions for gender discrimination violations and strengthen the defence of women &apos;s legitimate rights and interests .
In recent years , the Ningxia Women &apos;s Federation &apos;s Joint Department of Public Prosecutor &apos;s Office , Civil Affairs and other departments have made remarkable achievements in promoting and introducing specialized social forces to participate in the mediation of marital and family disputes and the anti-domestic violence work .
This is summarized in the Regulations , which encourage the mobilization of social forces and the pooling of social resources for the protection of women &apos;s rights and interests , and require the people &apos;s governments at and above the county level to provide stable , institutional protection and support through , for example , the purchase of services .
