Reporter 27 from the Yunnan Academy of Agricultural Sciences learned that at present , the grassland greedy night moths have been effective control , did not cause a large area outbreak into a disaster , prevention and control work to obtain periodic results .
In January this year , the grassland nocturia moth was first discovered from outside Jiangcheng County in Pu &apos;er City , Yunnan , and subsequently confirmed in 129 counties in Yunnan , spreading from Yunnan to the mainland of China , posing a direct threat to China &apos;s grain production .
The meadowland nocturnal moth is an important agricultural pest originating from tropical and subtropical areas of the Americas . It is a major migratory pest in the early warning of the United Nations Food and Agriculture Organization ( FAO ) worldwide and has the characteristics of &quot; international , migratory , sudden and destructive &quot; .
The pests harm more than 80 crops such as maize , sugar cane , sorghum , a large amount of food , can cause up to 70 % of production loss .
It is difficult to prevent and control the insect , and there is no registered pesticide in China .
Since the invasion of Yunnan , the Yunnan Academy of Agricultural Sciences has selected Chen Aidong to lead a team from the Yunnan Academy of Agricultural Sciences in collaboration with Green Prevention and Control to carry out field investigations , collect samples , and conduct technical instruction and experimental demonstration .
The Chen Aodong team has acquired the population characteristics , natural enemy insect resources , foreign insect source characteristics , population migration trajectory , toxicant and field control effects of Yunnan meadow nocturnal moth .
They have actively carried out research and application of green prevention and control technologies.Through the implementation of new green prevention and control technologies such as population monitoring , adult baiting , scientific drug use and agronomic measures , the prevention and control effect in the demonstration areas has reached over 90 percent , while the use of chemical pesticides has been reduced and the resources and ecological environment of natural enemies have been protected .
At present , Yunnan grassland greedy nocturnal moth has been effective control , did not cause a large area outbreak into a disaster , prevention and control work has obtained periodic results .
In the next step , Yunnan Academy of Agricultural Sciences will focus on the ecological mechanism of population migration invasion , breakthrough biological control and green control technology system construction .
At the same time , we will proactively promote cross-boundary international cooperation and strive to establish joint key laboratories and joint monitoring network sites and demonstration areas overseas to enhance the all-round monitoring and early warning capability of night moths in grasslands in Yunnan .
